modName: Marsha May Racemenu Preset AND Enhanced Character Edit Preset
summary: Racemenu Preset AND Enhanced Character Edit Preset of Marsha May(Pornstar)
descriptionHtml:
This is a Enhanced Character Edit and Racemenu Preset for Marsha May (pornstar).

If anyone knows how to change the eyebrow color please tell me. 

INSTALL
For Racemenu Users- Extract the file. In the folder drag the file in it to Skyrim Data/SKSE/Plugins/Chargen/Presets. IF YOU ARE USING MOD ORGANIZER drag the file to Mod Organizer/Overwrite/SKSE/Plugins/Chargen/Presets
If you do not have the Preset Folder then simply make one.(not sure if it works) but this other way does work. Go in Skyrim and in the console type in showracemenu. Complete your character then on the Upper right corner press presets. press F5 (default)to save your preset and name it if you wish to. Press done and exit out of showracemenu then the Preset  folder will appear. 

To use the preset go to showracemenu and press presets on the upper right corner. Press F9 (default)to load a preset. Choose Elly Tran Ha preset. and customize to your desire.

For Enhanced Character Edit Users- Extract the file. In the folder drag the file in it to My Documents/My Games/Skyrim/CME Save
If you do not have the CME Save folder simply make one.(including skse, plugins, and chargen folders but i'm not sure if it works) but this other way does work. Go in Skyrim and in the console type in showracemenu. Complete your character and press done. It will prompt you to save it as a slot or not. Save it. Then the CME Save folder will appear. 

To use the preset then go into showracemenu. Switch the Preset slider one time and it will prompt you with a menu. Choose Slot 10(you will have to press next on the menu). Then customize to your desire.
